### Prerequisites:

- Before requesting a device addition, please ensure there is not already a request for the device among the open issues.
- Make sure your Homey is upgraded to firmware v5 or higher.
- You need a physical example of the device.

### Device Information

- Device Name: `Tuya Zigbee Temperature Sensor`
- Device Model: `_TZ3000_1o6x1bl0 / TS0201`
- Device Description: `Battery-powered temperature measurement sensor for home automation`
- Link to device image: [[AliExpress Product Page](https://www.aliexpress.com/item/1005007920479552.html?spm=a2g0o.order_list.order_list_main.17.a64f1802A4pqAh#nav-specification)](https://www.aliexpress.com/item/1005007920479552.html?spm=a2g0o.order_list.order_list_main.17.a64f1802A4pqAh#nav-specification)

